void SET_TASK_MOVE_NETWORK_SIGNAL_FLOAT(Ped ped, char* signalName, float value);Parameters:ped: The ped on which the task is playing.signalName: The property name.value: The property value to set.p0 - PLAYER::PLAYER_PED_ID();
p1 - "Phase", "Wobble", "x_axis","y_axis","introphase","speed".
p2 - From what i can see it goes up to 1f (maybe).
